  "title": "Wings and Oak Leaves Aboard the Reprisal",
  "summary": "Aboard the carrier Reprisal, General Wedge Antilles presides over a New Republic StarOps promotion ceremony in the fighter hangar, awarding ranks and wings to the assembled Ghost Squadron pilots and support staff. With dry Corellian humor and personal touches, Wedge promotes Kyrin Sh'vani, Gene Malantean, Kesander Beysarus, Crystal Keldahoff, and Hase Stargazer, then theatrically dresses down Wing Commander Johmac Mabru before promoting him to Major and ordering him to buy the first rounds. Several cadets receive their wings, including a nod to Kensle Gravitz for bravery at the lost world of Cochran. Throughout, the pilots cheer one another while support techs and watching Marines enjoy the spirited proceedings, though the officer Elena grows visibly and inexplicably troubled. After a proud closing address, Wedge dismisses the ranks, and the newly promoted pilots head off toward the lounge to celebrate, with the tech Mitali approaching the withdrawn Elena to check on her.",
